<p><strong>A NEW EVENT DIMENSION</strong><br />Pure-liner offers access to the world of innovation and inspiration. Two unique sailing event locations for product presentations, exhibitions, kick off's and corporate parties.<br />The special architecture and modern presentation means offer an environment where you can welcome your guests in an extraordinary manner. Pure-liner welcomes its<br />guests in the Netherlands, Belgium and Germany! We can moor virtually anywhere where there's water.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>PURE-LINER 1</strong><br />The Pure-liner 1 has the German city of Cologne as its homeport. Cologne was a strategic choice, as the ship can call in at various major German town ports from<br />here. The ship has accommodated the most diverse types of events since its launch in 2005.</p>
